data.description: Welcome home to your own piece of paradise in the Southwest. This is an amazing 3 bed/3 bath custom home on 4.65 acres & has everything for your family, pets, horses & 4H animals. Property features several horse stalls, tack rooms, arena, Two fully fenced paddock areas & much more. Outbuildings with power & water, RV shelter with concrete pad, pool with Baja shelf. Home has had many upgrades and a list can be provided to you upon request. In the County but still close to all amenities, shopping & MCAS Yuma.
